Harry Harvey Sr. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Harvey_Sr. 0 Harry William Harvey Sr. (January 10, 1901 – November 27, 1985) was an American actor of theatre, film, and television. He was the father of actor, script supervisor, and director Harry William Harvey Jr..
